dash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"cd9662985a3ea2e8270f3c62372a6a8764e93746","tid":1342252,"uid":75398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"緊記，善用浮沉功能，見到垃圾POST，幾唔GUR都唔好，唔好負皮同留言，比佢沉"},{"pid":"8442d26d8121b58296d731f5972aa8a18da526e1","tid":1342252,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:13:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a3833576c865cb96c97d4bba161b600cfbc90d3","tid":1342252,"uid":169771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea94e9cc143b16972ed36edef4e6268eb9649423","tid":1342252,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e28efd75907827e2726467b451b4a5f6ff539fd","tid":1342252,"uid":259622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"屌你老母, 比人分化緊!!<br />\n721 推!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}